


Brian L. Roberts - Wikipedia






















 






Brian L. Roberts

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Brian L. Roberts





Born
(1959-06-28) June 28, 1959 (age 58)
Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, U.S.


Residence
Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, U.S.


