Brian L. Roberts - Wikipedia






















 






Brian L. Roberts

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Brian L. Roberts





Born
(1959-06-28) June 28, 1959 (age 58)
Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, U.S.


Residence
Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, U.S.


Nationality
United States


Education
Germantown Academy


Alma mater
Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania


Occupation
Chairman and CEO of Comcast


Salary
US$26.4 million (2014)


Net worth
 US$1.67 billion (March 2017)[1]


